WEBVTT

00:07:58.360 --> 00:08:02.536
I do not get this and am sure some of our
viewers would also like to know:

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:06.139
Can you tell us more if any one wants
to pursue home schooling in India?

00:08:06.139 --> 00:08:09.616
SJ: If you want to pursue homeschooling,

00:08:09.640 --> 00:08:12.880
I would just say don’t.

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:16.456
There is no support in India

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:19.296
and it is an uphill task to ...

00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:21.936
let’s say in grade 6

00:08:21.936 --> 00:08:25.216
if the child wants to change back
from homeschooling to formal school,

00:08:25.216 --> 00:08:27.600
then that door is completely
shut in this country.

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:30.966
So really think it through.
But in case you want more information,